      "cohort_label": "v19",
      "hypothesis": "age>10min + top5<10% is the new leaderboard #1 (n=117, opt +6.17% @ tp=150/sl=30, MODERATE wr_std_dev=10.6%, beats baseline by 17.4pp). Cohort tests three variants: v19-base mirrors the leaderboard exactly; v19-tight tightens top5 from <10% to <8% to test whether excluding moderate-concentration plays raises opt; v19-tp100 lowers TP from 150 to 100 to test whether earlier exits improve hit rate without losing too much per-win on live fills. At n=50 per variant, compare medians + SOL P&L; promote the strongest variant with stable regime.",
      "prediction": {
        "target_median_net_pct": 4,
        "target_n": 100,
        "target_days": 21,
        "kill_criterion": "n>=50 and median<-5"
      },
